column2: Whittaker's Creamy Milk 33% Cocoa Milk Chocolate Block 250g
column3:
Creamy Milk Chocolate (33% Cocoa)

Refined Swiss Craftsmanship. Pure New Zealand Creaminess.

Indulge in the perfect harmony of rich cocoa and creamy milk.
Our 33% cocoa milk chocolate is crafted using the finest Ghanaian cocoa beans and blended with 30% New Zealand milk powder for a luxuriously smooth finish.
To achieve its signature silky texture, it is refined using the traditional Swiss 5 Roll Refiner method – a testament to precision and perfection.

Key Features

  • 33% Cocoa Content: Made from premium Ghanaian cocoa

  • 30% NZ Milk Powder: Adds rich creaminess and smooth mouthfeel

  • Swiss 5 Roll Refining: Delivers a melt-in-your-mouth texture

  • 10 Servings per Pack: Conveniently portioned at 25g per serving

Ingredients

Milk Chocolate
Sugar, Cocoa Solids (33%) (Cocoa Butter, Cocoa Mass), New Zealand Milk Powder (30%), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Vanilla Flavour

Allergen Information

  • Contains: Milk, Soy

  • May Contain: Peanuts, Tree Nuts, Gluten

Nutritional Information

Nutrient Per 100g Per Serving (25g)
Energy 2,350kJ 590kJ
Protein 9.2g 2.3g
Total Fat 35.6g 8.9g
Saturated Fat 19.5g 4.9g
Carbohydrates 51.8g 13g
Sugars 44.7g 11.2g
Sodium 70mg 18mg

Serving Suggestions

Enjoy a square a day with your favorite cup of coffee or tea.
Store in a cool, dry place – avoid refrigeration to preserve texture.

column2: Whittaker's Creamy Caramel 33% Cocoa Milk Chocolate Block 250g
column3:
Silky Chocolate. Luscious Caramel. Pure Indulgence.

Discover pure satisfaction in every bite.
This 250g block combines our ultra-smooth 33% cocoa Creamy Milk Chocolate, made with the finest Ghanaian cocoa and 30% New Zealand milk powder, with a lusciously rich caramel center (34%).

The caramel is creamier, smoother, and more velvety than ever – making each bite an irresistible melt-in-the-mouth experience.

Why You'll Love It

  • 33% Cocoa Milk Chocolate: Crafted using Swiss 5 Roll Refining for ultimate smoothness

  • 34% Caramel Center: Made from real milk, butter, and natural flavourings for a buttery-sweet profile

  • Perfectly Portioned: 10 servings per block (25g each) – easy to share or savour slowly

Ingredients

Milk Chocolate:
Sugar, Cocoa Solids (33%) (Cocoa Mass, Cocoa Butter), New Zealand Milk Powder (30%), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Vanilla Flavour

Caramel (34%):
Glucose, Sweetened Condensed Milk, Milkfat, Sugar, Invert Syrup, Hydrogenated Coconut Oil, Salt, Natural Flavour, Acidity Regulator (Sodium Citrate), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin)

Allergen Information

  • Contains: Milk, Soy

column2: Whittaker's Peanut Caramel Brittle Creamy Milk Chocolate Block 250g
column3:
Creamy Milk Chocolate with Roasted Peanuts & Salted Butter Caramel Brittle (250g Block)

Crunchy. Buttery. Irresistible.

A bold twist on a timeless classic.

Our ultra-smooth 5 Roll Refined Creamy Milk Chocolate — made with 33% cocoa and 30% New Zealand milk powder — is generously packed with freshly roasted peanuts (24%) and crunchy salted butter caramel brittle (6%) for an unforgettable taste experience.

Each bite delivers a perfect balance of creamy, crunchy, sweet, and salty — a true treat for peanut lovers and chocolate connoisseurs alike.

Product Highlights

  • Made with 33% Cocoa & 30% NZ Milk Powder

  • Roasted Peanuts (24%): Fresh batch-roasted for rich, nutty crunch

  • Salted Butter Caramel Brittle (6%): Adds sweet and salty depth

  • Refined with Swiss 5 Roll Technology for melt-in-the-mouth smoothness

  • Rainforest Alliance Certified Cocoa: Ethically sourced ingredients

  • 10 Servings per Pack (25g each) – share or enjoy on your own!

Ingredients

Milk Chocolate:
Sugar, Cocoa Solids (33%) (Cocoa Butter, Cocoa Mass), NZ Milk Powder (30%), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Vanilla Flavour

Add-ins:

  • Roasted Peanuts (24%)

  • Salted Butter Caramel Pieces (6%): Sugar, Glucose, Butter (Milk), Salt, Water, Cocoa Butter, Natural Flavour, Natural Colours (100, 150A)

  • Natural Flavour

Minimum % Cocoa Solids & Milk Solids. All cocoa ingredients are Rainforest Alliance Certified.

Allergen Information

  • Contains: Milk, Soy, Peanuts

  • May Contain: Tree Nuts, Gluten

Snacking, gifting, or elevating your dessert tray. Enjoy with coffee, wine, or as a post-meal indulgence.
